title: Head to Hand ~ Teren has brought so much serenity and peace into my life. She is a dear friends daughter...

attachments.displayName:
Head to Hand ~ Teren has brought so much serenity and peace into my life. She is a dear friends daughter and I am blessed to share in these sweet moments together.

Teren reminds me that we are all living beings here to experience each other. To show loving kindness. When you feel into another being, feel the strength of their heart and the magnitude of power they posess but they choose a gentler way....... sweetness
